"Open Graph tags, per-space canonical URLs, breadcrumb schema, and advanced "
"robots control."
msgstr ""
"Open Graph-Tags, kanonische URLs pro Space, Breadcrumb-Schema und "
"erweiterte Robots-Steuerung."

